verbose_text: The correlations of H-18 to C-11, C-12 and C-13 and HO-13 to C-12 and C-14 established the connection of C-11-C-12-C-13-C-14, while the correlations of H-17 to C-11, C-12 and C-1, and H-2 to C-1 and C-11 indicated the presence of a five membered ring A. Subsequently, the correlations of H-9 to C-8 and H-10 to C-11 supported the connection of C-8-C-9-C-10-C-11.
